KARATE FIGHTER

This game is about upgrading your fighter by playing daily to become the best and training your fighter. Facing people nationwide across the world, it is an online game. 

 I  want to build some kind of game like this as well. But make it more female related as well intsead male audience, it can also attract the female audience as well. 
The interaction would be to use the mouse to click on different menu buttons
Move: W, A, S, D
Attacks: J, K, L, I
Combo Ability: U
Pause: P

To win is to basically beat the other opponent with a knockout and level up each time to face bigger opponents to become a martial arts champion. 


https://poki.com/en/g/karate-fighter

